Content:

Eh ngayong 2025, yung isang Senate bet ng DuterTen, Marites Mata ang nickname sa balota kahit na lalake siya.

Mga hipokrito talaga mga Duterte.#Halalan2025

Content:
When Richard Gomez ran for Senator in 2007, he joined a senatorial election forum on ANC. In his closing remarks, he asked voters not to vote for him  "dahil artista siya".

An interesting statement, considering how he was nowhere near the Top 12 in the surveys.#Halalan2025
